WEBVTT

00:00:09.933 --> 00:00:13.533
( broadcast music playing )

00:00:13.533 --> 00:00:15.033
Announcer:
THE WINNER OF TONIGHT'S MATCH

00:00:15.033 --> 00:00:16.666
WILL CONTINUE ON TO FACE YURI,

00:00:16.666 --> 00:00:19.833
WHO WON A DECISIVE K. O.
JUST A FEW DAYS AGO.

00:00:19.833 --> 00:00:22.700
WILL "GEARLESS" JOE,
WHO SLID INTO THE FINAL SLOT,

00:00:22.700 --> 00:00:24.633
ENDURE THE ONSLAUGHT
OF GLEN BURROUGHS

00:00:24.633 --> 00:00:26.766
AND PULL OFF
ANOTHER MIRACULOUS WIN?

00:00:26.766 --> 00:00:30.533
EXPECTATIONS ARE HIGH AFTER
HIS DEFEAT OF MIKIO SHIRATO,

00:00:30.533 --> 00:00:32.733
AND NOT JUST
WITH MEDIA EXPERTS, EITHER.

00:00:32.733 --> 00:00:35.433
EVEN THE EXACTING STANDARDS
OF OVERSEAS BOOKMAKERS

00:00:35.433 --> 00:00:37.633
ARE PREDICTING
A VICTORY FOR JOE.

00:00:37.633 --> 00:00:40.566
THE CURRENT ODDS ARE LISTED
BETWEEN 3‐TO‐1 AND 5‐TO‐1.

00:00:40.566 --> 00:00:42.900
‐ ( turns off radio )
‐ ( phone chirping )

00:00:42.900 --> 00:00:44.966
( Nanbu groans )

00:00:44.966 --> 00:00:46.200
YEAH?

00:00:46.200 --> 00:00:47.533
Fujimaki: AMAZING, ISN'T IT?

00:00:47.533 --> 00:00:48.800
YOU'VE GOT
THE WHOLE WORLD FOOLED

00:00:48.800 --> 00:00:50.166
WITH THIS SCAM OF YOURS.

00:00:50.166 --> 00:00:53.733
Nanbu: I DON'T REMEMBER
ASKING FOR ANY PROTECTION.

00:00:53.733 --> 00:00:56.066
Fujimaki: MY APOLOGIES
IF THEY PUT YOU OFF.

00:00:56.066 --> 00:00:58.500
I'M SURE YOU'LL DO
THE RIGHT THING.

00:01:00.166 --> 00:01:02.173
SEE YOU AT THE ARENA.

00:01:06.606 --> 00:01:07.940
HMM.

00:01:07.940 --> 00:01:09.673
( heart beating )

00:01:20.073 --> 00:01:22.173
( tires squeal )

00:01:24.906 --> 00:01:26.673
♪

00:01:37.973 --> 00:01:39.673
( singing in Japanese )

00:02:54.780 --> 00:02:54.946
( birds chirping )

00:02:57.013 --> 00:02:58.613
( birds chirping )

00:03:03.986 --> 00:03:06.086
( Sachio grunts )

00:03:06.086 --> 00:03:08.220
THEY WERE OUT BY THE DUMPSTER,
SO I JUST THOUGHT...

00:03:08.220 --> 00:03:09.786
Yukiko: THAT'S VERY KIND.

00:03:09.786 --> 00:03:12.220
Sachio: JUST PAYING YOU BACK
FOR THE ROOM AND ALL THE FOOD.

00:03:12.220 --> 00:03:14.986
I DON'T WANNA END UP
HAVING TO OWE YOU ANYTHING.

00:03:14.986 --> 00:03:17.320
Yukiko: I COULD NEVER
TAKE CARE OF FLOWERS.

00:03:17.320 --> 00:03:20.153
THEY ALWAYS DIE
BEFORE THE PETALS FALL. EH?

00:03:22.653 --> 00:03:23.986
IS THAT A GOOD LUCK CHARM?

00:03:23.986 --> 00:03:25.520
( Sachio gasps )

00:03:25.520 --> 00:03:27.653
WELL, I'M LOOKING
AFTER JOE'S I. D., SO...

00:03:27.653 --> 00:03:30.253
Yukiko: YOU MADE THAT
WITH HIM IN MIND?

00:03:32.520 --> 00:03:34.153
Sachio: TO BE HONEST...

00:03:34.153 --> 00:03:35.920
MY MOM LIKED THESE FLOWERS.

00:03:35.920 --> 00:03:37.253
( Yukiko gasps )

00:03:38.786 --> 00:03:41.753
YOU CAN STILL JOIN ME, YOU KNOW.
COME ON. THERE'S TIME.

00:03:41.753 --> 00:03:44.486
Sachio: I'M NOT GOING!
I'VE MADE UP MY MIND, OKAY?!

00:03:44.486 --> 00:03:47.853
Yukiko: DON'T YOU WANT
TO SEE EVERYTHING FIRSTHAND,

00:03:47.853 --> 00:03:50.053
JOE STANDING IN THE RING
AT MEGALONIA?

00:03:50.053 --> 00:03:52.853
Sachio: I DON'T NEED
TO SEE HIM TO KNOW!

00:03:52.853 --> 00:03:55.453
JOE WON'T LOSE
BEFORE HE FIGHTS YURI!

00:03:55.453 --> 00:03:57.053
( Yukiko gasps )

00:03:57.053 --> 00:03:58.953
( door opens, closes )

00:03:58.953 --> 00:04:01.026
I SEE.

00:04:01.026 --> 00:04:03.093
WELL, WE ALL HAVE
CHOICES TO MAKE.

00:04:07.960 --> 00:04:09.926
( overlapping chatter )

00:04:11.560 --> 00:04:13.826
♪

00:04:23.193 --> 00:04:26.160
Ring announcer: GLEN BURROUGHS!
THE HEAVYWEIGHT BOXER

00:04:26.160 --> 00:04:29.826
WHO STALKS THE RING LIKE
A LION STALKS THE WASTELANDS.

00:04:29.826 --> 00:04:31.660
FACING THIS WILD BEAST,

00:04:31.660 --> 00:04:33.993
THE MAN WHO FIGHTS
WITH NOTHING BUT HIS FISTS,

00:04:33.993 --> 00:04:35.793
THE UNARMED HUNTER...

00:04:35.793 --> 00:04:38.226
♪

00:04:49.560 --> 00:04:52.893
THE MAN WHO'S SCORED
UPSET AFTER MIRACULOUS UPSET

00:04:52.893 --> 00:04:57.226
WITH NO ENHANCEMENT,
"GEARLESS" JOE!

00:05:06.533 --> 00:05:09.166
( blows striking bag )

00:05:09.166 --> 00:05:11.000
Sachio: HEY, JOE,
I WAS WONDERING.

00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:12.800
WHAT DO YOU DO
WHEN YOU'RE SCARED?

00:05:12.800 --> 00:05:14.133
Joe: HUH?

00:05:14.133 --> 00:05:16.266
Sachio: LIKE WHEN YOU'RE
AFRAID TO MAKE A MOVE

00:05:16.266 --> 00:05:17.333
AND YOU FREEZE UP.

00:05:18.733 --> 00:05:19.900
I WANNA‐‐

00:05:19.900 --> 00:05:23.700
I WANNA BE ABLE
TO FIGHT ON MY OWN, TOO.

00:05:24.933 --> 00:05:27.000
Joe: TOUCH SOMETHING AROUND YOU.

00:05:27.000 --> 00:05:28.633
DOESN'T MATTER WHAT IT IS.

00:05:28.633 --> 00:05:29.400
Sachio: HUH?

00:05:29.400 --> 00:05:31.033
Joe: IT HELPS YOU FOCUS,

00:05:31.033 --> 00:05:33.166
PUTS YOU IN THE MOMENT.

00:05:33.166 --> 00:05:35.833
IT REMINDS YOU
OF WHAT YOU NEED TO DO.

00:05:37.700 --> 00:05:39.966
THAT'S A TRICK I LEARNED
A LONG TIME AGO.

00:05:39.966 --> 00:05:42.466
IT'S PROBABLY
A LOAD OF CRAP, THOUGH.

00:05:42.466 --> 00:05:43.700
Sachio: WHAT THE HELL?

00:05:43.700 --> 00:05:46.366
WHO TAUGHT YOU
THAT BUNCH OF NONSENSE?

00:05:46.366 --> 00:05:48.300
( overlapping chatter )

00:05:57.933 --> 00:05:59.533
Yukiko: UH, ONE MOMENT, PLEASE.

00:05:59.533 --> 00:06:01.740
WOULD YOU LIKE ANYTHING?

00:06:01.740 --> 00:06:02.973
Yuri: NO.

00:06:02.973 --> 00:06:04.973
Yukiko: VERY WELL.
THANK YOU. YOU CAN GO.

00:06:04.973 --> 00:06:06.206
Server: MY PLEASURE, MA'AM.

00:06:10.873 --> 00:06:14.606
PARDON ME.
I'VE BROUGHT YOUR MEAL.

00:06:14.606 --> 00:06:15.640
( gasps )

00:06:16.840 --> 00:06:17.840
( door closes )

00:06:21.906 --> 00:06:23.806
Gangster: ALL OUR CUSTOMERS
ARE BUYING THE HYPE

00:06:23.806 --> 00:06:25.773
AND BETTING ON JOE,
JUST AS WE HOPED.

00:06:25.773 --> 00:06:28.140
UNFORTUNATELY FOR THEM,
HE'S GOING DOWN

00:06:28.140 --> 00:06:30.073
IN HIS FIRST MATCH
OF THE TOURNEY.

00:06:30.073 --> 00:06:33.006
WRAP IT UP IN THE THIRD ROUND
WITH A MINUTE TO GO.

00:06:33.006 --> 00:06:35.740
HAVE HIM PUT ON A GOOD SHOW
UP 'TIL THEN.

00:06:37.440 --> 00:06:41.306
Fujimaki: THIS WATER'S GOT
A HARDNESS OF OVER 600 P. P. M.

00:06:41.306 --> 00:06:45.606
IT GOES EXCEPTIONALLY WELL WITH
FISH THAT'S BEEN BOILED IN IT.

00:06:45.606 --> 00:06:47.740
SEE, THE THING ABOUT HARD WATER

00:06:47.740 --> 00:06:50.206
IS THAT IT MAKES
FOR A GREAT STOCK.

00:06:56.740 --> 00:06:59.946
Ring announcer: AND NOW LET'S
WELCOME TONIGHT'S FIGHTERS!

00:06:59.946 --> 00:07:01.846
♪

00:07:01.846 --> 00:07:03.546
IN THE EAST CORNER,

00:07:03.546 --> 00:07:05.746
THE THIRD‐RANKED I. M. A. FIGHTER,

00:07:05.746 --> 00:07:08.446
REPRESENTING
THE KILLER BOMB CREW...

00:07:08.446 --> 00:07:12.513
GLEN "BLOODY LION" BURROUGHS!

00:07:12.513 --> 00:07:15.346
( crowd cheering )

00:07:20.213 --> 00:07:22.346
( Burroughs roars )

00:07:25.580 --> 00:07:27.680
Ring announcer:
AND IN THE WEST CORNER,

00:07:27.680 --> 00:07:30.013
THE FOURTH‐RANKED
I. M. A. FIGHTER,

00:07:30.013 --> 00:07:32.646
REPRESENTING TEAM NOWHERE,

00:07:32.646 --> 00:07:36.713
FAN FAVORITE "GEARLESS" JOE!

00:07:36.713 --> 00:07:39.346
( crowd cheering )

00:07:42.680 --> 00:07:43.546
Man: HUH?

00:07:43.546 --> 00:07:44.746
Man #2: GO GET 'EM, "GEARLESS."

00:07:46.346 --> 00:07:48.213
Man #1: HEY, IS THAT...

00:07:48.213 --> 00:07:49.880
Man #2: WHAT'S GOING ON?

00:07:49.880 --> 00:07:51.313
Man #3: YOU GOTTA BE KIDDING ME!

00:07:52.780 --> 00:07:54.346
Announcer: LOOKS LIKE WE'VE GOT

00:07:54.346 --> 00:07:56.046
AN INTERESTING TURN HERE, FOLKS,

00:07:56.046 --> 00:07:59.380
AN INCONCEIVABLE TWIST
FOR THE WORLD OF MEGALO‐BOXING.

00:07:59.380 --> 00:08:01.020
"GEARLESS" JOE, WHOSE RING NAME

00:08:01.020 --> 00:08:03.686
HAS ALWAYS REFLECTED HIS LACK
OF FIGHTING‐ENHANCING EQUIPMENT,

00:08:03.686 --> 00:08:05.753
STEPPED INTO THE ARENA
EQUIPPED WITH GEAR.

00:08:05.753 --> 00:08:07.453
Commentator:
IT COULD BE A STRATEGY TO COPE

00:08:07.453 --> 00:08:09.820
WITH THE POWER DISADVANTAGE
HE HAS FIGHTING BURROUGHS.

00:08:09.820 --> 00:08:11.353
Announcer:
THAT IS A POSSIBILITY.

00:08:11.353 --> 00:08:12.920
PLUS, IT SEEMS THAT, THIS TIME,

00:08:12.920 --> 00:08:16.053
JOE WILL BE FIGHTING ALONE,
WITH NO ONE IN HIS CORNER.

00:08:16.053 --> 00:08:18.253
( Nanbu grunts )

00:08:18.253 --> 00:08:21.786
Fujimaki: LOOKS LIKE YOU'VE GOT
HIM TRAINED WELL, COACH NANBU.

00:08:25.853 --> 00:08:28.586
Nanbu: I'M NOT GONNA ASK
FOR FORGIVENESS, JOE.

00:08:28.586 --> 00:08:31.086
HELL, I DON'T EVEN DESERVE IT.

00:08:32.986 --> 00:08:36.186
YOU PROBABLY DON'T EVEN
WANNA HEAR MY VOICE,

00:08:36.186 --> 00:08:38.920
BUT I'M COUNTING ON YOU.

00:08:38.920 --> 00:08:41.353
WE'RE GONNA THROW THE MATCH
IN THE THIRD ROUND.

00:08:41.353 --> 00:08:43.953
YOU GOTTA HOLD OUT UNTIL THEN.

00:08:43.953 --> 00:08:47.286
Burroughs: WELL, NOW, YOU PUT ON
THAT GEAR JUST FOR ME?

00:08:47.286 --> 00:08:48.220
I'M HONORED.

00:08:48.220 --> 00:08:50.186
WHAT A CHICKEN.

00:08:50.186 --> 00:08:52.586
YOU AND
THAT SLEAZY GEAR OF YOURS

00:08:52.586 --> 00:08:54.753
ARE ABOUT TO GET
SMASHED INTO GARBAGE.

00:08:54.753 --> 00:08:56.386
( horn blows )

00:08:56.386 --> 00:08:58.220
‐ ( crowd cheering )
‐ ( Burroughs grunts )

00:08:58.220 --> 00:09:01.626
Yukiko: WHY WOULD HE WEAR GEAR
IN THE RING AFTER ALL THIS TIME?

00:09:03.893 --> 00:09:06.560
Yuri: WHY?

00:09:06.560 --> 00:09:08.593
Man: CHECK IT OUT.
HE'S GOT GEAR ON.

00:09:08.593 --> 00:09:10.393
Man #2: SO? HE'S ALL TALK.

00:09:10.393 --> 00:09:11.760
Man #3: DON'T CHICKEN OUT!

00:09:11.760 --> 00:09:13.160
( Sachio grunts )

00:09:13.160 --> 00:09:14.193
Santa: SACHIO!

00:09:14.193 --> 00:09:16.660
WHAT THE HELL'S GOING ON, MAN?!

00:09:16.660 --> 00:09:19.060
Oicho: BIG JOE'S
IN THE RING WEARING GEAR,

00:09:19.060 --> 00:09:20.926
AND YOU AND POPS
AREN'T OUT THERE WITH HIM.

00:09:20.926 --> 00:09:23.293
Bonjiri: WE'RE MORE
THAN A LITTLE CONFUSED.

00:09:23.293 --> 00:09:24.293
Santa: SACHIO!

00:09:24.293 --> 00:09:26.126
( Sachio grunts )

00:09:26.126 --> 00:09:27.793
I'M DONE WITH THIS.

00:09:29.026 --> 00:09:30.660
‐ Santa: HUH?
‐ Bonjiri: HUH?

00:09:32.160 --> 00:09:32.860
Oicho: SACHIO?

00:09:35.160 --> 00:09:36.526
( Joe groans )

00:09:38.293 --> 00:09:39.593
Nanbu: DON'T POKE HIM TOO MUCH.

00:09:39.593 --> 00:09:40.660
HE'LL JUST COME AFTER YOU.

00:09:47.426 --> 00:09:49.626
HE RELIES TOO MUCH ON HIS POWER,

00:09:49.626 --> 00:09:51.593
SO HE NEVER STEPS IN
DEEP ENOUGH.

00:09:51.593 --> 00:09:53.493
USE YOUR LEGS. GET AROUND HIM.

00:09:57.160 --> 00:09:58.760
I SAID USE THOSE LEGS,

00:09:58.760 --> 00:10:00.766
OR ELSE HE'S
GONNA SMASH YOUR GEAR!

00:10:00.766 --> 00:10:02.000
DAMN.

00:10:04.200 --> 00:10:06.333
Sachio: WHO CARES
ABOUT "GEARLESS" JOE?

00:10:06.333 --> 00:10:07.800
WHO CARES
ABOUT WINNING IT ALL?

00:10:07.800 --> 00:10:09.466
THIS WHOLE THING IS A SCAM!

00:10:14.066 --> 00:10:15.133
( Burroughs laughs )

00:10:15.133 --> 00:10:16.400
Nanbu: WATCH IT!

00:10:16.400 --> 00:10:18.133
HE'S GONNA COME AT YOU HARD!

00:10:23.233 --> 00:10:24.833
( horn blows )

00:10:24.833 --> 00:10:28.000
Announcer: AND THAT'S
THE END OF THE FIRST ROUND!

00:10:28.000 --> 00:10:30.966
I HAVE TO SAY,
DESPITE HAVING A BETTER SHOWING,

00:10:30.966 --> 00:10:34.533
BURROUGHS WAS CERTAINLY LOOKING
A BIT APPREHENSIVE OUT THERE.

00:10:34.533 --> 00:10:35.833
Commentator:
YEAH, I SAW IT, TOO.

00:10:35.833 --> 00:10:38.666
JOE HAS THE BOXING SENSE
TO KEEP HIM IN THE GAME

00:10:38.666 --> 00:10:42.033
AND THE STRENGTH TO TURN
A MATCH AROUND WITH ONE HIT.

00:10:42.033 --> 00:10:43.333
Gangster #2: HMPH.

00:10:43.333 --> 00:10:45.966
THAT COCKY LITTLE SHIT
BETTER NOT BE TRYING TO WIN.

00:10:45.966 --> 00:10:47.600
Gangster #3: I'LL BET
HE'S JUST TUNING OUT

00:10:47.600 --> 00:10:48.966
EVERYTHING THAT YOU'RE SAYING.

00:10:48.966 --> 00:10:51.866
Nanbu: IF JOE WAS
REALLY TRYING TO BEAT HIM,

00:10:51.866 --> 00:10:55.700
HE'D HAVE KNOCKED HIS LIGHTS OUT
RIGHT AFTER THAT BODY BLOW.

00:10:55.700 --> 00:10:58.100
IT DOESN'T MATTER IF HE'S
LISTENING TO ME OR NOT.

00:10:58.100 --> 00:11:01.073
HE'S DOING THE JOB
AND KEEPING THE FIGHT LIVELY.

00:11:01.073 --> 00:11:02.473
( chuckles )

00:11:02.473 --> 00:11:04.640
I DOUBT YOU GUYS
CAN SEE THAT, THOUGH.

00:11:04.640 --> 00:11:05.906
‐ Gangster #3: HMM?
‐ Gangster #2: HUH?

00:11:05.906 --> 00:11:07.906
YOU BETTER WATCH YOUR MOUTH,
YOU WASHED‐UP FAT‐ASS‐‐

00:11:07.906 --> 00:11:09.706
Fujimaki: IT'S A HELL
OF A PERFORMANCE.

00:11:09.706 --> 00:11:13.040
FIRST, HE MISSES BURROUGHS
ON PURPOSE.

00:11:13.040 --> 00:11:15.140
THEN HE'S ONLY
SLIGHTLY OFF‐MARK.

00:11:15.140 --> 00:11:16.673
IT'S BRILLIANT.

00:11:16.673 --> 00:11:19.440
NO ONE WILL REALIZE
HE'S THROWING THE MATCH.

00:11:19.440 --> 00:11:21.473
YOU'VE BEEN
GIVING HIM INSTRUCTIONS

00:11:21.473 --> 00:11:23.673
TO HELP HIM AVOID GETTING HURT,

00:11:23.673 --> 00:11:26.173
BUT HE'S BEEN GOING
COMPLETELY AGAINST THAT

00:11:26.173 --> 00:11:27.940
AND TAKING PUNCHES ON PURPOSE.

00:11:27.940 --> 00:11:29.406
( Nanbu groans )

00:11:29.406 --> 00:11:30.906
Fujimaki: YOUR STRAY DOG'S
DEFYING YOU.

00:11:30.906 --> 00:11:34.473
I GUESS HE'S TELLING YOU
HE DOESN'T NEED YOUR ADVICE.

00:11:35.640 --> 00:11:37.773
( crowd cheering )

00:11:37.773 --> 00:11:39.473
♪

00:11:43.640 --> 00:11:46.273
Joe: I WANNA FIGHT YOU
IN A REAL MATCH,

00:11:46.273 --> 00:11:48.106
PURE AND SIMPLE.

00:11:48.106 --> 00:11:49.773
I THINK, AGAINST YOU,

00:11:49.773 --> 00:11:52.673
I'D GO FURTHER
THAN I'VE EVER GONE BEFORE.

00:11:54.006 --> 00:11:55.806
( Yuri grunts )

00:11:59.073 --> 00:11:59.346
♪

00:12:01.613 --> 00:12:04.080
♪

00:12:04.080 --> 00:12:06.613
( crowd cheering )

00:12:06.613 --> 00:12:08.913
Announcer: IT'S EARLY
IN THE SECOND ROUND,

00:12:08.913 --> 00:12:12.546
AND I'VE NOTICED BURROUGHS SEEMS
TO BE THROWING FEWER PUNCHES.

00:12:12.546 --> 00:12:14.146
Commentator:
HE'S BEING CAUTIOUS, SMART.

00:12:14.146 --> 00:12:16.613
JOE'S SHOWN A KNACK
FOR THROWING COUNTERPUNCHES.

00:12:19.713 --> 00:12:22.713
Nanbu: DON'T! YOU GOTTA
KEEP IT GOING PAST THIS ROUND!

00:12:25.980 --> 00:12:28.013
DID YOU HEAR ME, KID?

00:12:28.013 --> 00:12:29.713
LISTEN TO ME FOR ONCE, DAMN IT!

00:12:30.946 --> 00:12:32.746
YOU WON'T LAST
IF YOU KEEP THIS UP!

00:12:41.146 --> 00:12:42.546
BLOCK AND MOVE TO THE SIDE.

00:12:46.613 --> 00:12:49.413
THERE YOU GO. THAT'S THE WAY.

00:12:49.413 --> 00:12:51.846
THE BIG LUG
CAN'T KEEP UP WITH YOU.

00:12:51.846 --> 00:12:54.646
SLOW HIM DOWN WITH A SOLID
BODY SHOT AFTER HE PUNCHES,

00:12:54.646 --> 00:12:56.480
THEN GIVE HIM A HOOK
OVER HIS SHOULDER.

00:13:01.020 --> 00:13:01.986
HELL, YEAH!

00:13:03.153 --> 00:13:04.520
Fujimaki: HMM.

00:13:05.920 --> 00:13:07.620
( horn blows )

00:13:07.620 --> 00:13:10.520
Announcer: SO FAR, JOE IS
PUTTING UP ONE HELL OF A FIGHT.

00:13:10.520 --> 00:13:11.853
I THINK THAT'D BE THE CASE

00:13:11.853 --> 00:13:14.353
WITH OR WITHOUT THAT GEAR
HE FINALLY PUT ON.

00:13:14.353 --> 00:13:15.453
Commentator:
TRUE, BUT REMEMBER,

00:13:15.453 --> 00:13:17.286
THERE WAS NO ONE ACTING
AS HIS SECOND.

00:13:17.286 --> 00:13:18.586
PERHAPS THERE WAS A DISPUTE

00:13:18.586 --> 00:13:20.220
ABOUT HOW
HE SHOULD FIGHT TONIGHT.

00:13:20.220 --> 00:13:21.486
( Nanbu sighs )

00:13:21.486 --> 00:13:22.520
Fujimaki: THINGS ARE
QUITE DIFFERENT

00:13:22.520 --> 00:13:24.320
SINCE THE UNDERGROUND DAYS.

00:13:24.320 --> 00:13:25.920
Nanbu: BURROUGHS IS
TOUGH AS HELL.

00:13:25.920 --> 00:13:28.753
HIS THIRD‐PLACE RANKING
IS WELL DESERVED,

00:13:28.753 --> 00:13:31.320
BUT IF JOE
COULD FIGHT HIM FOR REAL...

00:13:31.320 --> 00:13:32.920
Fujimaki: I'M TALKING ABOUT YOU.

00:13:32.920 --> 00:13:35.720
YOU'RE ACTING
LIKE A REAL TRAINER.

00:13:35.720 --> 00:13:37.686
‐ Nanbu: EH?
‐ Gangster #1: MR. FUJIMAKI,

00:13:37.686 --> 00:13:39.986
MOST OF THE BETS
ARE COMING IN FOR JOE.

00:13:39.986 --> 00:13:41.286
THE ODDS HAVE GONE UP AGAIN.

