Sachio: HEY! LET GO!
WHAT THE HELL, MAN?!

00:17:17.213 --> 00:17:18.180
Guard: JUST CUFF HIM.

00:17:18.180 --> 00:17:19.580
Sachio: LET ME GO, YOU ASSHOLES!

00:17:22.880 --> 00:17:24.946
( guard #2 stammering )

00:17:24.946 --> 00:17:28.846
Yuri: YOU HAVEN'T FORGOTTEN
WHAT YOU TOLD ME, HAVE YOU?

00:17:28.846 --> 00:17:30.446
( Joe gasping )

00:17:35.613 --> 00:17:39.446
Yuri: DO NOT DISAPPOINT ME.
UNDERSTAND?

00:17:49.880 --> 00:17:52.413
‐ Nanbu: GET UP!
‐ ( Joe gasps )

00:17:52.413 --> 00:17:54.746
Nanbu: ON YOUR FEET, JOE!

00:17:54.746 --> 00:17:56.513
♪

00:17:56.513 --> 00:18:00.053
NO ONE'S GONNA LAY A FINGER
ON SACHIO. GOT IT?!

00:18:00.053 --> 00:18:04.353
AND NOBODY'S GONNA
TAKE TOMORROW FROM YOU!

00:18:05.353 --> 00:18:08.720
GET UP. GET UP, AND FIGHT.

00:18:08.720 --> 00:18:11.986
THIS IS IT!
YOUR TOMORROW'S COMING, JOE!

00:18:13.520 --> 00:18:16.053
YOU'VE GOT THE TRUE SKILLS
OF A CHAMPION,

00:18:16.053 --> 00:18:19.020
AND THAT'S
A GANSAKU NANBU GUARANTEE.

00:18:19.020 --> 00:18:22.586
YOU'RE NOT TAKING FALLS ANYMORE.

00:18:22.586 --> 00:18:25.853
Computer: 7, 8...

